OL,5, Younger and lower-paid workers should  
OL,6, be included in a scheme which sees     
OL,7, people automatically enrolled into     
OL,8, pension saving, a think tank says.     
OL,10,FCurrent rules require workers aged 22  
OL,11,Fand above to be enrolled, and receive a
OL,12,Fcontribution from their employer, when 
OL,13,Fthey earn more than #10,000 a year.    
OL,15,FThe Social Market Foundation (SMF) says
OL,16,Fthose from minority ethnic backgrounds 
OL,17,Fdisproportionately miss out.           
OL,19,FThe government says it is planning to  
OL,20,Fmake these changes, when affordable.   
